channel.title: Project Helios Server Development!
channel.description:
[center][b][i][size=16pt]Welcome to Project Helios![/size][/i][/b][/center]
[size=12pt][center][b][i][color=purple]About Us-[/center] [center][color=teal][i]Well i'm starting Project Helios 317 because I miss the good old days of RuneScape. I chose the 317 revision because it was one of my favorite times on RuneScape, the quests, PKing, old falador and barbarian village is some of my favorite parts about it. The server will be based of Apollo by Graham, the reason I have selected this source is because of the lack of usage as it's fairly new, and to expand not only my knowledge, but my teams knowledge. We plan on emulating everything in that revision from minigames such as CastleWars, to EVERY skill working 100%.[/center]
